### More on day trends

By the first plot, it shows that student population appears to be pulling the high volume trend on Friday. When this is broken down by affiliations, both Mailman and SON have the highest request volume on Thursday; however, VP&S’s request shows a high concentration on Fridays. 

```{r, echo=FALSE, warning=FALSE}
dayRole <- with(infoApr20_CLN_noClass, table(role, day))
dayRole <- as.data.frame(dayRole)

dayRole <- dayRole %>% filter(role == "Student" | role == "Faculty" | role == "Postdoc Fellow" | 
                                role == "Staff")

