### Methodology

The trend of Systematic Review being the most popular methodology persists in April, 2020. It is noteworthy that 5 tickets are regarding scoping review, a trend not observed in March, 2020. Also, about 11% of clients are unsure of which review to conduct. This suggests that providing continued guidance on review types and  revamping of  [A Comparison of Reviews](https://library.cumc.columbia.edu/sites/default/files/page/A%20Comparison%20of%20Reviews.pdf) may be helpful.  We also noticed a trend of “neither review nor quant” was a close second to Systematic Review.  This means that about half of our clients seek our services for general literature search strategies.  

```{r, include=FALSE}
