### Project type 

In April 2020, the most popular project type was publication. Considering that most of the clients who submitted inquiries regarding publications in March 2020, were clients from CBCH or SON, it follows that there would be a similar breakdown in April 2020. However, the clients who identified their project type as publications varies from students to staff. Also, thesis and dissertation related inquiries are high volume this month, which makes sense in terms of the upcoming May commencement. 

```{r, include=FALSE}
